A clone of v2ex, and more.
Layout/css is based on v2ex.


software required:
1. python....2.6+
2. mongodb...latest.
3. redis...latest.

Lib required:
1. twisted http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/
2. cyclone https://github.com/fiorix/cyclone
3. async mongodb driver https://github.com/fiorix/mongo-async-python-driver
4. recaptcha http://pypi.python.org/pypi/recaptcha-client
5. WebHelpers http://pypi.python.org/pypi/WebHelpers/1.3
6. feedparse  http://www.feedparser.org/
7. pymongo  https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-python-driver  for db migrate.
8. cPickle  for redis serialization/de

Start:
1. start mongodb, redis
2. add some dummy data: python test.py
3. dev run: python run.py -ny app.py
4. prod run: twistd -n(y) app.py

